profile:
New Leaf Decor is an established Home Staging/Interior Redesign Company proudly serving Barrie, Newmarket, North York and beyond. Offering in depth, comprehensive staging consultations is the first step, then developing an action plan to ensure the home shows at its very best. New Leaf Decor has a vast inventory of artwork, rugs, decor and staging accessories, and if furniture is necessary, we have many resources to accommodate. New Leaf Decor also has a large list of trusted trades people to cover any needs. (Painters, window cleaners, house cleaners, handyman services, etc) 
Many of my staging clients love the way their homes looked when staged that they end up hiring me to create the same look in their new homes. This is what is called Interior Redesign, using your existing furniture in a new way. Adding new, updated elements such as artwork, rugs, lamps and decor to create a fresh, redesigned space affordably. Of course if new furniture is needed, I have many preferred pricing partners, including Hunter Douglas Blinds.
